Fan-project disclaimer
======================

This is an unofficial, non-commercial, fan-made bug-fix patch for **Pokémon
Ash Gray**, a ROM hack of Pokémon FireRed created by **metapod23**. It is not
affiliated with, endorsed by, or supported by metapod23, Nintendo, Game Freak,
The Pokémon Company, or any rights holder.

- **No copyrighted ROM data is distributed here.** This repository contains
  only a patch (`patches/ashgray-fork.ips`), source/analysis tooling, and
  documentation. The patch is a binary diff; it does not include the FireRed
  ROM or metapod23's hack.

- **You must supply your own legally-obtained game.** To use this, apply the
  IPS patch to a clean Pokémon FireRed (USA) v1.0 ROM that you own. See README
  / RELEASE.md for the exact hashes and steps.

- **Credit.** Pokémon Ash Gray and all of its original content are the work of
