- **No warranty.** Use at your own risk. Back up your saves. See the caveats in
  RELEASE.md (e.g. the box-reserve mitigation protects new saves, not ones that
  already have a Pokémon in a hazard box).

If a rights holder objects to this fan patch, open an issue and it will be
taken down.
